{"slug":"sirkuler-26-0280","reference":"Sirkuler_26_0280","gazette":"08 Mayıs 2026 Tarihli ve 33247 Sayılı Resmî Gazete","title":"Teknoloji Hamlesi Programı Uygulama Usul ve Esaslarında Değişiklik Yapıldı","date":"08 Mayıs 2026","bodyHtml":"<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Sanayi ve Teknoloji Bakanlığı tarafından\r\nyayımlanan Tebliğ ile, “Teknoloji Hamlesi Programı Uygulama Usul ve Esasları\r\nTebliği”nde önemli değişikliklere gidildi.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Yapılan düzenlemeler kapsamında öne çıkan\r\nhususlar aşağıda yer almaktadır:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">“Üretime\r\nyönelik yatırım süreci” ve “yatırım projesi” tanımları yeniden düzenlenerek;\r\nteşvik belgesi kapsamındaki faaliyetlerin yanı sıra TÜBİTAK ve KOSGEB destekli\r\nproje faaliyetleri de kapsam içine alındı. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Tebliğin\r\nüçüncü bölüm başlığı değiştirilerek proje komisyonu, proje paydaşı ve Ar-Ge\r\nyüklenicisine ilişkin yapı güncellendi. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Komitenin\r\ndestek başvurularına ilişkin kararlarının, 13/C maddesindeki kriterler\r\nçerçevesinde puanlama yöntemiyle alınacağı hüküm altına alındı. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Tebliğin 8\r\ninci maddesi yürürlükten kaldırıldı. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Proje\r\nkomisyonlarının oluşumu, görevleri ve değerlendirme süreçleri yeniden\r\ndüzenlendi. Buna göre; <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Komisyonlar en az birer TÜBİTAK, KOSGEB ve\r\nTUYSGM temsilcisinden oluşacak, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">İhtiyaç halinde bağımsız değerlendiriciler\r\ngörevlendirilebilecek, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Komisyon raporları ve ek bilgi-belgelerin\r\nProgram Portaline yüklenmesi zorunlu olacak. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Başvuru\r\nsahibi ile proje paydaşı arasındaki iş birliği, Komite değerlendirmesinde\r\npuanlama kriteri olarak dikkate alınacak hale getirildi. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Başvuruların\r\ndetaylı inceleme aşamasında Tebliğ veya çağrı planı şartlarını sağlamadığının\r\ntespiti halinde, başvuruların değerlendirme dışı bırakılabileceği ve bu\r\nkararlara karşı 15 iş günü içinde itiraz edilebileceği düzenlendi. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Ön\r\ndeğerlendirme kriterleri yeniden belirlenirken; <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Projenin çağrı planına uygunluğu, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Proje sistematiği ve tutarlılığı, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Emsal ürün ve iyi uygulama örneklerine\r\nuygunluğu, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Aynı konuda açık teşvik belgesi bulunup\r\nbulunmadığı<br>\r\nkriterleri esas alınacak. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Eksik belge\r\nveya açıklamaların tamamlatılması amacıyla yatırımcıya 5 ila 15 gün arasında\r\nrevizyon süresi verilebilecek. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">İzleme\r\nekspertizi ve tamamlama süreçlerine ilişkin hükümler güncellendi. Yatırım\r\nilerleme raporlarının izleme yükümlülüğünü ortadan kaldırmayacağı açıkça\r\ndüzenlendi. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Başarısız\r\ntamamlandığı tespit edilen projelerin Program kapsamından çıkarılması ve fazla\r\nsağlanan destek unsurlarının geri alınmasına ilişkin usuller yeniden\r\ndüzenlendi. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Tebliğ yayımı tarihinde yürürlüğe girmiş olup\r\nhükümlerini Sanayi ve Teknoloji Bakanı yürütmektedir.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;display:none;mso-hide:all\">Formun Üstü<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;\">Kaynak:</span>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.resmigazete.gov.tr/eskiler/2026/05/20260508-14.htm\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">https://www.resmigazete.gov.tr/eskiler/2026/05/20260508-14.htm</a></p>\n                                <a target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-danger\" href=\"\">\n                                    \n                                </a>"}
